# Automatic Dates Examples in Zolt

## Basic Date Variables

Using automatic date variables:

This document was created on: {$created}
Last modified: {$modified}

## Date Formatting with Date.format()

Use the `Date.format()` function to format dates:

**Date only:** {{ Date.format($created, "DD/MM/YYYY") }}
**Date and time:** {{ Date.format($modified, "DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm") }}
**ISO format:** {{ Date.format($created, "YYYY-MM-DD") }}

## Format Tokens

Available format tokens:

| Token  | Description      | Example |
|--------|------------------|---------|
| `DD`   | Day (2 digits)   | 23      |
| `MM`   | Month (2 digits) | 02      |
| `YYYY` | Year (4 digits)  | 2026    |
| `YY`   | Year (2 digits)  | 26      |
| `HH`   | Hour (24h)       | 14      |
| `mm`   | Minutes          | 30      |
| `ss`   | Seconds          | 45      |

## Common Date Formats

### ISO Format

Created: {{ Date.format($created, "YYYY-MM-DD") }}

### European Format

Created: {{ Date.format($created, "DD/MM/YYYY") }}

### US Format

Created: {{ Date.format($created, "MM/DD/YYYY") }}

### Custom Format

Created: {{ Date.format($created, "DD MMM, YYYY") }}

## Practical Examples

### Document Header

# My Document

**Created:** {{ Date.format($created, "DD MMMM YYYY") }}
**Last Updated:** {{ Date.format($modified, "DD MMMM YYYY à HH:mm") }}

### Version History

## Version History

| Version | Date                                       | Changes                    |
|---------|--------------------------------------------|----------------------------|
| 1.0.0   | {{ Date.format($created, "YYYY-MM-DD") }}  | Initial release            |
| 1.1.0   | {{ Date.format($modified, "YYYY-MM-DD") }} | Bug fixes and improvements |

### Blog Post

# Post Title

**Published:** {{ Date.format($created, "MMMM DD, YYYY") }}

### Technical Report

**Report Generated:** {{ Date.format($created, "DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm") }}

## Multiple Date Formats in Same Document

**Short format:** {{ Date.format($created, "DD/MM/YYYY") }}
**Long format:** {{ Date.format($created, "DD MMMM, YYYY") }}
**Full datetime:** {{ Date.format($created, "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss") }}
**Compact:** {{ Date.format($created, "YYYYMMDD") }}

## Combining with Other Functions

### With String Functions

Year: {{ String.upper(Date.format($created, "YYYY")) }}
Compact date: {{ String.replace(Date.format($created, "YYYY-MM-DD"), "-", "") }}

### With Math Functions

Timestamp in seconds: {{ Math.floor($created / 1000) }}

### In Conditional Blocks

:::if {{ $modified > $created }}
*This document has been updated since creation.*
Last update: {{ Date.format($modified, "DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm") }}
:::

